{"word":"G2616 - καταδυναστεύω - katadynasteúō - kat-ad-oo-nas-tyoo'-o - Oppress","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταδυναστεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katadynasteúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ad-oo-nas-tyoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Oppress</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஒடுக்கு, அகப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to exercise harsh control over one, to use one's power against one: to oppress one"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G1413 - δυνάστης - dynástēs - doo-nas'-tace/1413\">G1413</a>; to <i>exercise dominion against</i>, that is, <i>oppress:</i> - oppress.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}